Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:31.64,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}E inocentemente sorrimos enquanto embarcamos nele
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:31.64,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Nokkatta boku-ra wa mujaki ni warau
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:36.56,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Existem placas em todos os lados em que olhamos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:36.56,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Migi-hidari nigiyaka na sign ga afurete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:42.61,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Podemos confiar em você se nos perdermos, motorista?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:42.61,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Mayottara mi o makasu desu yo ne, driver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:52.33,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Será que ainda haveriam crimes se não existisse mais maldade?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:52.33,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Waruginakutemo tsumi wa umaremasu ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:58.79,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Onde está a resposta? Alguém sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:58.79,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Kotae wa doko ni kakusarete'ru no somebody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:05.01,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Não desista, pense um pouco mais! Questione! Responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:05.01,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Akiramenaide mō choi kangaete Question! Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:16.48,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Toque seu rosto enquanto estiver na escuridão
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:16.48,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\1a}Kurayami ni ukande'ru sono hoho ni fureru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:28.20,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}E agarre a justiça que ninguém pode abandonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:28.20,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\1a}Daremo ga yuzurenai seigi o idaite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:33.87,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}A resposta sempre esteve aqui! Tudo mundo sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:33.87,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Kotae wa koko ni chanto aru ja nai everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:39.75,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Mas mesmo com ela, eu sei que muitos corações ainda vão duvidar!\N — Questione! Responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:39.75,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Sakedo mō hitotsu kokoro ga harenai Question! Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:44.63,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}{\fad(0,1000)}E teremos que continuar vivendo com esta tristeza\N — Questione! Responda!
